title: Laos Food Inflation
description: Cost of food in Laos increased 38.80 percent in October of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Food Inflation in Laos averaged 5.47 percent from 2013 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 38.80 percent in October of 2022 and a record low of -2.11 percent in December of 2017. This page provides - Laos Food Inflation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Lao Statistics Bureau
